pageContext.collection_title: Camp Fire, ca.1910-ca.1994 and n.d., bulk 1950s-1980s
pageContext.collection_description: Collection relates to the activities, membership and administration of the Lincoln, NE chapter of the youth group Camp Fire (formerly known as Camp Fire Girls) and includes photographs, scrapbooks, moving images and approximately 40 sound recordings. Check with repository for more information about radio related material in the collection.
